#                                                                              #
# Dependencies:                                                                #
#                                                                              #
#   - Ag/Telescope                                                             #
#   - bash                                                                     #
#   - find                                                                     #
#   - fzf                                                                      #
#   - jq                                                                       #
#   - vim/nvim                                                                 #
#   - sed                                                                      #
#   - sort                                                                     #
#   - tail                                                                     #
#   - tr                                                                       #
#                                                                              #
# Purpose:                                                                     #
#                                                                              #
#   - Create/Edit notes in LaTeX with Vim/Neovim                               #
#                                                                              #
# Last changed:                                                                #
#                                                                              #
#   Goi√¢nia, 07 de fevereiro de 2025                                           #
